{"tid":895026,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"急救CPR。係。唔。使。check。脈。搏。","createTime":"2018-11-09T00:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T10:04:37.000Z","uid":138409,"like":25,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"095cdce37da45d64c13fa5cf2453a5489095c2d5","tid":895026,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T00:28:41.000Z","msg":"轉載自「一個平凡醫學生的日常。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/medstudenthk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmedstudenthk%2F&d=Oghd3ciEbQH%2B5GyYlYTWV5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=33df8c10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/medstudenthk/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9wYe9wW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9wYe9wW.jpg&h=482fd226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x7Wz9w2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx7Wz9w2.jpg&h=652018c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉載自M19同學Tom：<br />\n<br />\n任何人，包括「任何仁」及其他未受急救訓練的人士，<span style=\"color: red;\">只要確認患者不省人事以及沒有正常呼吸，不需要檢查脈博，就可以施行心外壓來拯救患者</span>。假如袖手旁觀，便會錯過搶救患者的黃金時間，患者會因失救而死。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有任何心外壓的副作用比死亡更嚴重。</span></span>另外，現時的自動體外心臟去顫器（AED）能自動辨識需要電擊的心臓節奏並進行除顫，急救者無需擔心「電錯人」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">法例沒有要求施行心外壓的途人擁有任何證書或專業資格。</span><br />\n<br />\n《施行心外壓之前需要檢查脈博嗎？》<br />\n研究發現未受急救訓練的人士及醫護人員同樣在檢查脈博時遇到困難。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">故此途人只要確認患者不省人事以及沒有正常呼吸，不需要檢查脈博，就可以施行心外壓來拯救患者。</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">【補充Guideline原文：／／ If the patient is unresponsive with abnormal or absent breathing, it is reasonable for the emergency dispatcher to assume that the patient is in cardiac arrest (Class IIa, LOE C-LD). ／／】</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n《如何施行心外壓？》<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">心肺復甦法的步驟很簡單，在緊急情況下（如突發心臟驟停），即使未受過專業訓練亦應施行。</span>進行心肺復甦法前應確保現場環境安全，再檢查患者清醒程度。若患者失去意識，首先要請旁人致電「九九九」報警，以及取得自動體外心臟去顫器。與此同時，應嘗試打開患者氣道及確保氣道暢道。若患者沒有呼吸，應盡快開始進行心外壓。若取得自動體外心臟去顫器，應按自動體外心臟去顫器上的指示接駁至患者身體。<br />\n<br />\n除了以上流程，進行心肺復甦法時亦需要注意以下要點：<br />\n* 按壓時掌根應緊貼胸骨下半部<br />\n* 按壓速率應為每分鐘一百至一百二十次。<br />\n* 按壓的深度至少要有五厘米。按壓期間手臂應保持挺直。<br />\n* 每次按壓後，<span style=\"color: red;\">要讓胸部完全反彈</span>，以便血液回流心臟。<br />\n* 按壓時應盡量避免停頓。<br />\n<br />\nReference: <br />\nKleinman ME, Brennan EE, GoldbergerZD, et al. Adult basic life support andcardiopulmonary resuscitation quality: 2015 American Heart Association Guidelines Update for Cardiopulmonary Resuscitation and Emergency Cardiovascular Care. Circulation 2015;132:S414&ndash;35 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ahajournals.org/doi/pdf/10.1161/CIR.0000000000000259?fbclid=IwAR2xTc0weLLl4x9dSMQi1Q-4RHv7fuQuvL3f95vyEGWUA0VfnSENXOk57K0&amp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ahajournals.org%2Fdoi%2Fpdf%2F10.1161%2FCIR.0000000000000259%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2xTc0weLLl4x9dSMQi1Q-4RHv7fuQuvL3f95vyEGWUA0VfnSENXOk57K0%26&d=Oghd3ciEbQH%2B5GyYlYTWV5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=2e651129\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ahajournals.org/doi/pdf/10.1161/CIR.0000000000000259?fbclid=IwAR2xTc0weLLl4x9dSMQi1Q-4RHv7fuQuvL3f95vyEGWUA0VfnSENXOk57K0&amp;</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O0dVTW8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO0dVTW8.png&h=73cc10bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c520c0c3079561a10903fa7e48ac4d17977d572b","tid":895026,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T00:36:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7c6e2a65865c6a6378f90b5b28be0265ba353849","tid":895026,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T00:36:51.000Z","msg":"你唔好噉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09a959a37e35710cfce47cc97caae59857b65a3","tid":895026,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T00:38:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"043b8dfab6